title: Coyotes "A Flecha": Rubber Tracks Live
description:
Brazilian three-piece Coyotes rocked the crowd during their opening set for Brand New on night 2 of Converse Rubber Tracks Live Brasil.

For more on Converse Rubber Tracks:
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks

Venue: Cine Joia
